(delete the myenv folder before proceeding pls, thanks)

tasks: https://docs.google.com/document/d/1l4042pvM1hyVcgFehPWMndJWrhuAcQlfXOYdNwWxhSo/edit?usp=sharing

1 -- VENV STUFF
WINDOWS:
python -m venv myenv
myenv\Scripts\activate

MACOS:
python3 -m venv myenv
source myenv/bin/activate

2 -- INSTALL
cd backend
pip install -r requirements.txt

!! OTHER COMMANDS
-- START VENV
source myenv/bin/activate

-- STOP VENV
deactivate

-- START BACKEND
cd into backend/config
python manage.py runserver (make sure ur venv is running)

-- IF FRONT END NEED DEPDENCIES IN THE BEGINNING, DO
yarn

-- STARTING FRONTEND
yarn start

---SUPERUSER for when you go localhost:8000/admin
user: test
pass: test
(not creative, i know thanks)

git pull --rebase origin main

RESOURCES I USED TO IMPLEMENT GOOGLE AUTH:
